<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= data.title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/intro.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="intro-container">
  <h1 class="intro-title"><%= data.title %></h1>

  <p class="intro-desc">
    젤리경찰청은 각 전문 부서가 유기적으로 협력하여 시민 안전을 책임집니다.
  </p>

  <% data.teams.forEach(team => { %>
    <div class="dept-box">
      <div class="dept-title"><%= team.name %></div>
      <div class="dept-text"><%= team.desc %></div>
    </div>
  <% }) %>
</div>

</body>
</html>
